# <ul>
# <li>INPUT: Input metadata records to process.</li>
# </ul>
# <p><strong>Output Ports</strong> </p>
# <ul>
# <li>DATA_OUTPUT: The process output metdata records.</li>
# </ul>
# <p><strong>Parameters</strong> </p>
